254
00:22:53.164 --> 00:22:54.082
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Don't forgetâ€¦</font></i>

255
00:22:56.751 --> 00:22:57.627
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">that you're the oneâ€¦</font></i>

256
00:23:03.341 --> 00:23:04.550
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">who killed me.</font></i>

257
00:23:36.332 --> 00:23:43.339
{\an8}THE LATE LEE SU-HO
MAY 7. 1991 - JUNE 14. 2018

258
00:24:00.022 --> 00:24:02.150
FAITHFUL TO DUTY. FAITHFUL TO THE PEOPLE

259
