in Kim Yun-ji's accident and yours.

262
00:24:11.701 --> 00:24:14.245
If we catch 4549.
we'll find out who's behind it.

263
00:24:14.912 --> 00:24:17.331
Fine. let's find the ghost car first

264
00:24:17.415 --> 00:24:18.749
and argue again later.

265
00:24:18.833 --> 00:24:20.418
How about we team up like old times?

266
00:24:20.501 --> 00:24:22.503
You cover the west side of Sanjun-dong.
and I'll cover the east side.

267
00:24:23.087 --> 00:24:23.921
All right.

268
00:25:30.696 --> 00:25:32.615
SANJUN JUNKYARD

269
00:25:50.174 --> 00:25:51.008
JUNKYARD

270
00:25:51.092 --> 00:25:52.009
Jeez. he's fast.

271
00:25:54.262 --> 00:25:55.680
I think it's that one over there.

272
00:25:59.308 --> 00:26:00.309
Hey.

273
