279
00:26:51.319 --> 00:26:53.988
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">You're approaching your destination.</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Ending navigation.</font></i>

280
00:26:54.071 --> 00:26:55.906
{\an8}ALPHA TOWER

281
00:27:03.456 --> 00:27:06.792
He's good-looking. tall. well-educated.

282
00:27:06.876 --> 00:27:08.878
