283
00:27:09.503 --> 00:27:11.422
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">What brought you here</font></i>

284
00:27:12.465 --> 00:27:13.758
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">at this particular time?</font></i>

285
00:27:19.597 --> 00:27:23.225
YOUR HOME
CEO PAEK JUN-BEOM

286
00:28:01.013 --> 00:28:02.264
I'm Paek Jun-beom.

287
00:28:04.683 --> 00:28:06.811
Nice to meet you. I'm Paek Jun-beom.

288
00:28:07.478 --> 00:28:08.646
I see you're left-handed.

289
00:28:09.688 --> 00:28:12.066
Oh. I use it out of habit.

290
00:28:33.629 --> 00:28:35.005
Is this good enough?

291
00:28:38.008 --> 00:28:39.343
