292
00:28:40.553 --> 00:28:41.637
What's this?

293
00:28:42.930 --> 00:28:46.851
Well. I thought our plan was still on.

294
00:28:49.395 --> 00:28:50.229
Oh.

295
00:28:57.194 --> 00:28:58.237
You're right.

296
00:28:58.320 --> 00:29:00.739
In that case. I should react like this.

297
00:29:14.003 --> 00:29:15.087
Anyway.

298
00:29:15.171 --> 00:29:16.088
here you go.

299
00:29:16.797 --> 00:29:17.965
It's your birthday. after all.

300
00:29:19.383 --> 00:29:20.217
Thank you.

301
00:29:22.511 --> 00:29:23.387
Come on in.

302
00:29:34.315 --> 00:29:36.066
