318
00:30:53.018 --> 00:30:54.186
Really?

319
00:31:00.359 --> 00:31:01.652
Just look at the color.

320
00:31:08.242 --> 00:31:09.493
-Is it good?
-It's delicious.

321
00:31:11.870 --> 00:31:12.913
Cheers.

322
00:31:19.295 --> 00:31:21.714
