386
00:37:43.136 --> 00:37:44.846
-Hello?
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">-Mr. Cha.</font></i>

387
00:37:44.930 --> 00:37:47.349
Mr. Lee Kwang-jin woke up.
They're moving him to a regular ward.

388
00:37:48.850 --> 00:37:49.935
