395
00:38:08.245 --> 00:38:11.415
The police are suspicious of you.
and I don't want you to get in trouble.

396
00:38:13.709 --> 00:38:15.669
Okay. call me.

397
00:39:29.993 --> 00:39:34.956
LEE *****-JIN

398
00:42:10.779 --> 00:42:11.738
Are you sleeping?

399
00:42:12.906 --> 00:42:14.866
You should've followed him!

400
00:42:14.950 --> 00:42:17.244
Do you know how scary this was?

401
00:42:18.578 --> 00:42:20.538
Did you do as I said?

402
00:42:20.622 --> 00:42:21.581
Yes.

403
00:42:25.377 --> 00:42:26.753
Jeez. you scared me.

404
00:42:29.756 --> 00:42:30.966
What theâ€¦

405
00:42:37.013 --> 00:42:38.139
That littleâ€¦

406
00:42:42.018 --> 00:42:43.311
This bastard is 4549.

407
00:42:43.395 --> 00:42:45.689
I knew I could do it!

408
00:42:48.400 --> 00:42:50.110
