If it weren't for your foresight.

415
00:43:34.779 --> 00:43:37.157
Mr. Lee Kwang-jin
would've been in real danger.

416
00:43:38.033 --> 00:43:39.075
Where is he right now?

417
00:43:39.576 --> 00:43:40.952
Up there.

418
00:43:41.036 --> 00:43:41.911
Way up high.

419
00:43:44.998 --> 00:43:47.459
AHN *****-SOO

420
00:43:53.506 --> 00:43:54.966
Do you recognize him?

421
00:43:55.550 --> 00:43:57.010
Yes. that's Jun-beom.

422
00:44:19.407 --> 00:44:20.700
Were these taken in Syria?

423
00:44:22.911 --> 00:44:24.788
They were like brothersâ€¦

424
00:44:25.705 --> 00:44:27.123
before that accident.

425
00:44:28.875 --> 00:44:30.168
The whole refugee camp

426
00:44:30.710 --> 00:44:32.796
was completely destroyed
in the air strike that day.

427
00:44:33.671 --> 00:44:35.340
Su-ho died on the spot.

428
00:44:35.924 --> 00:44:38.593
and Jun-beom barely survived.

429
00:44:40.261 --> 00:44:42.180
After being brought to Korea for surgery.

430
00:44:42.263 --> 00:44:43.556
