00:47:54.914 --> 00:47:56.082
chose to end his life.

451
00:48:07.885 --> 00:48:08.803
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Don't forgetâ€¦</font></i>

452
00:48:11.431 --> 00:48:12.473
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">that you're the oneâ€¦</font></i>

453
00:48:16.144 --> 00:48:17.437
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">who killed me.</font></i>

454
00:48:23.276 --> 00:48:25.278
I couldn't bring myself to tell you

455
00:48:25.361 --> 00:48:26.863
because I was afraid you'd say

456
00:48:27.697 --> 00:48:29.616
I manipulated Su-ho into killing himself.

457
00:48:30.700 --> 00:48:32.035
