You missed the rest of what I said.

462
00:48:49.510 --> 00:48:52.263
I only meant that's how detectives
might view things.

463
00:48:53.848 --> 00:48:54.807
You got it all wrong.

464
00:48:56.184 --> 00:48:58.186
I don't suspect you anymore.

465
00:48:58.269 --> 00:48:59.228
I believe you.

466
00:49:00.813 --> 00:49:03.232
That's why I'm telling you everything.

467
00:49:06.361 --> 00:49:10.239
He kept saying he was going to die.
so I just told him to dieâ€¦

468
00:49:12.408 --> 00:49:13.910
and to stop bothering me.

469
00:49:15.411 --> 00:49:16.579
If only I hadn't said that

470
00:49:18.247 --> 00:49:19.832
on our last callâ€¦

471
00:49:20.375 --> 00:49:21.709
Don't blame yourself.

472
00:49:24.045 --> 00:49:25.838
It wasn't your fault.

473
00:49:28.174 --> 00:49:30.093
I think I know why he sent this.

474
00:49:31.469 --> 00:49:36.599
Mr. Paek is seeking revenge
on Su-ho's behalf.

475
00:49:38.518 --> 00:49:40.144
He's using every means possible

476
00:49:40.978 --> 00:49:42.814
