477
00:49:48.236 --> 00:49:49.404
Since he gave you a gift.

478
00:49:51.072 --> 00:49:52.365
we should give him one in return.

479
00:49:58.579 --> 00:50:00.415
DNA MATCH
VEHICLE 4549. EVIDENCE IN ATTEMPTED MURDER

480
00:50:00.498 --> 00:50:02.333
The same DNA was collected

481
00:50:02.417 --> 00:50:04.377
